{"title":"热","authors":["王开炳"],"dates":[{"year":1984,"month":9,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"热"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王开炳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光和热向车内辐射，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驾驶室象蒸笼格。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶篷如盖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"座垫如铁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沥青路，晒出了油，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是那样腻，是那样黑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽车从上面驶过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下了一道道深沉的辙……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车轮在梦的记忆里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"探索着美的彩色；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人，在历史的长河中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寻找着象水力一样释放光和热。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管，落日以句号提出运转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新月以顿号暗示间歇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可司机的满腔豪情呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成了潜在的“核”……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}